OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA warm end
OL,6,Fto the day with some late evening
OL,7,Fsunshine. Staying dry overnight with
OL,8,Fmostly clear skies at first, and some
OL,9,Fpatchy cloud. A cool night for many,
OL,10,Fparticularly further north.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FPatchy cloud around to start
OL,13,Fthe day, but turning increasingly
OL,14,Fsunny through the morning. Light
OL,15,Fnortherly winds, slightly stronger
OL,16,Falong the coasts. Feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
