OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FStaying largely dry with sunny spells
OL,7,Fand variable amounts of cloud. A few
OL,8,Fspots of rain are possible at times
OL,9,Fwhere the cloud thickens. Temperatures
OL,10,Faround the seasonal average.
